						               													<description>The game &amp;quot;Obstsalat&amp;quot; (=fruit salad) was included in Spielbox 1/87 as part of the &amp;quot;Spiel zum Herausnehmen/Game to Remove&amp;quot; series.&amp;#10; The board is divided into 4 parts. Each part is the playing sector of one of the 2-4 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Object of the game is to move all 6 playing pieces to the final space in the middle of the board. The first player reaching this, is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Movement is done by throwing 2 dice, one normal die and one colour die. The normal die determines the number of spaces a playing piece can move, the color die enables the use of shortcuts of the appropriate color, though throwing black lets the piece move backwards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Jumping over pieces is not allowed and landing on an occupied space lets the piece go back to the start.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
